  <brief_title>The Effect of the Combined Use of Naloxone and Tramacet on Postoperative Analgesia in the Elderly</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of the Combined Use of Naloxone and Tramacet on Postoperative Analgesia in Elderly Patients Having Joint Replacement Surgery: a Prospective Feasibility Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
